comments: Spends most of her time trying to convince people that she does things for her students, but then she won\'t meet any student representative from ASI, including student senators from her own college - apparently she\'s just too "busy," more so than even the university\'s president. Demonstrates clear disdain and contempt for students.
YOU CAN\'T HIDE YOUR HATE, Laura Kingsford Hill, Dean of the College of Natural Science and Math and supporter of California Proposition 8
Least enthusiastic, least motivating public speaker ever.
